# Example O1 Windows Authenticode evidence

Copy to `../windows-sig.txt` only after a real Authenticode signature on the freeze build.
This example file is **not** gather PASS evidence.

```
subject: CN=EXAMPLE — replace with real Authenticode subject
thumbprint: 0000000000000000000000000000000000000000
file: dist/1.0.0/windows-x64/trareon-lab.exe
sha256: REPLACE_WITH_FILE_SHA256
signtool_verify: PASS
timestamp: REPLACE_UTC
operator: REPLACE
host: ThinkPad reference (see docs/WINDOWS-LAB-QUEUE.md W3)
```
